      "writtenOn": "2021-03-31T16:40:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is not a possible XSS reflection vector, httputils.ReportError calls\nhttp.Error which sets the following headers:\n\n\tw.Header().Set(\"Content-Type\", \"text/plain; charset\u003dutf-8\")\n\tw.Header().Set(\"X-Content-Type-Options\", \"nosniff\")\n\nWe do need the errors returned in production so users can debug\nwhy their docs are not rendering.",
